 The season where it might snow, but it doesnâ€™t, so insects were thankfully less active.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;There were pests like flies, but parasite activity was also inhibited. It was tough to keep in mind not bringing back fleas or ticks that have jumped onto you.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;The hunter cut open the bear, which was facing up and drained of blood, from its throat. After cutting the esophagus, he next sliced up from the anus.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œUgh.â€ One of the new court physicians disappeared due to the stench of blood and organs.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Yao endured with bloodshot eyes.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;How is Changsha doing?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Changshaâ€™s complexion was bad, but not to the point of vomiting. The girl watched the dismantling without averting her eyes.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Perhaps to save on time, or because it was too much responsibility for one person, three people were in charge of the dismantling. It seemed messy, but they were skilled at taking out the organs without damaging them. One person diligently poured water, flushing away the blood to improve visibility.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;The extracted organs were stuffed into a large pail. There were also organs tossed into a small pail.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œWeâ€™ll be taking these,â€ a blood-covered hunter said.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œGot it. Weâ€™ll borrow this place for the time being.â€&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œSure. Make sure to wash away the blood completely.â€&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;The hunters carried away the bear that had been broken down into meat and pelt, as well as the small pail.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;The organ pieces left behind gave off a foul smell.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œNow then, itâ€™s our turn,â€ Wanwan-senpai said.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œO-OUR TURN?!â€ a young court physician said.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œYes.â€&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;His tone left no room for discussion.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Maomao, accustomed to it, carefully laid out the organs on the boulder where they had done the dissection. â€œPeople with cuts on their hands, please refrain from touching blood or the organs. You will get sick.â€&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Since it was cold, the parasites were suppressed, but they were inside wild animals all year round.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œThose too scared to touch can go ladle water over or something.â€ Wanwan-senpai went over to the young court physicians. For a moment, the court physicians made looks of frustration, but two meekly went off to draw water.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Maomao, while laying out the organs, tilted her head at the damaged sections. â€œDo they intend to eat those as a delicacy?â€ she asked.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;The missing cuts were probably in the small pail.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œIt should be fine if they get cooked,â€ Wanwan-senpai said.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;That being said, it would be difficult for the teacher if there werenâ€™t enough teaching materials.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œCome to think of it,â€ he looked at the sky. â€œWeâ€™ll have to stay overnight at this rate. Would that be alright with you?â€&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œI am fine with that,â€ Maomao said. â€œHow about you two? Should we reserve lodgings too?â€&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œPlease.â€&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;The sun would probably set while they received an explanation of the organs.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-right wp-block-paragraph"&gt;(&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/15-06-baby-deer-baby-boar-baby-bear-2/"&gt;Next Chapter&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div id="jp-post-flair" class="sharedaddy sd-like-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-official sd-sharing"&gt;&lt;h3 class="sd-title"&gt;Share this:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="sd-content"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="share-facebook"&gt;&lt;div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/15-05-baby-deer-baby-boar-baby-bear-1/" data-layout="button_count"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="share-end"&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-130534757-5614-697a826a96cd8' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/index.html?ver=20260128#blog_id=130534757&amp;amp;post_id=5614&amp;amp;origin=shikarito.wordpress.com&amp;amp;obj_id=130534757-5614-697a826a96cd8' data-name='like-post-frame-130534757-5614-697a826a96cd8' data-title='Like or Reblog'&gt;&lt;div class='likes-widget-placeholder post-likes-widget-placeholder' style='height: 55px;'&gt;&lt;span class='button'&gt;&lt;span&gt;Like&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class='loading'&gt;Loading&amp;#8230;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class='sd-text-color'&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class='sd-link-color' href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/15-05-baby-deer-baby-boar-baby-bear-1/"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/main&gt;</description>
