was no precedent.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Conversely, now that there was a precedent, it was probably easy to have Changsha participate.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;When they finished examining the bearâ€™s organs, they processed the useful parts. There was bearâ€™s gall, a medicine sourced from bears, but its other parts also had uses.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œI wonder if they could spare us some bear fat,â€ a court physician with relatively practiced hands said. He wasnâ€™t a first timer, having participated several times before.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œWe had no agreement to obtain fat, but why do you ask?â€ Wanwan-senpai asked.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œItâ€™s nothing much. I just heard that applying it to your hair will help with hair growth.â€&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œReally?â€ Wanwan-senpai was also interested.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;It seems that when gentlemen pass a certain age, they end up becoming creatures concerned about their hair.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Maomao splashed water onto the boulder after they had dealt with the innards. She scrubbed away at the smeared blood as she rinsed it off. It was so cold that her fingers were numb.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œUgh.â€&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Yao and Changsha did the same, scrubbing away with straw. Yaoâ€™s hands were chapped. No matter how much she moisturised, her hands were bound to end up like that if she was washing up every single day.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œYou guys, wash up properly as well,â€ Wanwan-senpai said to the new court physicians. They joined in.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Among them, some remained sitting, still feeling unwell, and some refused to work, stating that cleaning wasnâ€™t 