€œâ€œâ€¦â€â€ Maomao and Changsha exchanged glances.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œSorry, but may I sleep on the floor?â€ Yao said.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œI&amp;#8217;m sorryâ€¦â€ Maomao said.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;This was the result of weighing between sleeping on the same bed as the young lady, and having her sleep on the floor. Either would incur wrath, but sharing a bed with her would put their lives in danger.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;â€œYes! I will be sleeping on the floor!â€ Yao was oddly proud about it.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;sup&gt;T/N: Happy New Year!&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-right wp-block-paragraph"&gt;(Next Chapter)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div id="jp-post-flair" class="sharedaddy sd-like-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-official sd-sharing"&gt;&lt;h3 class="sd-title"&gt;Share this:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="sd-content"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="share-facebook"&gt;&lt;div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/15-06-baby-deer-baby-boar-baby-bear-2/" data-layout="button_count"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="share-end"&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-130534757-5623-697a84952474f' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/index.html?ver=20260128#blog_id=130534757&amp;amp;post_id=5623&amp;amp;origin=shikarito.wordpress.com&amp;amp;obj_id=130534757-5623-697a84952474f' data-name='like-post-frame-130534757-5623-697a84952474f' data-title='Like or Reblog'&gt;&lt;div class='likes-widget-placeholder post-likes-wi