eed/"&gt;Horny Goat Weed&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/ss-the-villa-1/"&gt;The Villa Part 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/ss-the-villa-2/"&gt;The Villa Part 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-dots" /&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center wp-block-paragraph"&gt;And then we have a writing exercise that&amp;#8217;s &lt;em&gt;probably&lt;/em&gt; not canon.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/ss-untitled/"&gt;Untitled&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center wp-block-paragraph"&gt;This one is technically not WN, but a side story nonetheless. It was released to commemorate the end of the anime&amp;#8217;s 2nd season (to the wider audience at least). Chronologically set near the end of LN4.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/ss-sazens-secret/"&gt;Sazen&amp;#8217;s Secret&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div id="jp-post-flair" class="sharedaddy sd-like-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-official sd-sharing"&gt;&lt;h3 class="sd-title"&gt;Share this:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="sd-content"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="share-facebook"&gt;&lt;div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/" data-layout="button_count"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="share-end"&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class='sha